{"tid":715563,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(轉貼)[事件還原+高登公投]會員做個快樂人被Bam一事","createTime":"2018-06-24T14:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T10:11:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25e9e68602804268fbbceab6b94303e09aa9107b","tid":715563,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"呢幾日望到支持做個快樂人嘅會員同唔支持佢嘅會員大家口同鼻拗，唔知頭唔知路盲中中噉對罵，仲要唔同posts都係講有關嘅嘢，我只好整合成件事再直接搞一次公投算。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事緣 : 22/6 下晝嗰時突然成個時事台畀會員做個快樂人 (#301682) 嘅posts佔領，第一版同第三版幾乎有半1/3嘅posts都係來自佢，然後有唔同巴打開posts投訴點解成個時事台都係佢啲posts，懷疑因為做個快樂人 (#301682)個帳畀admin ban咗，之後一本道 (#283926)最終要喺返呢個帳度為自己平反，開咗個「尋日時事台洗版非「做個快樂人」所為，係有人不斷推佢ｐｏ」嘅posts反擊一眾狙擊佢嘅user。一本道喺post入面言之鑿鑿噉話做個快樂人 (#301682) 最多每次都係推三至四個posts，大家喺時事台見到洗版情況係會員莘辛學子 (#596295) 同 戀屍神父 (#583602)陷佢於不義，設局做佢。 <br />\n<br />\n而家等我同大家還原真相。22/6下晝12點幾，做個快樂人(#301682) 將自己喺半個月內開過唔同台嘅posts隨機地 / 將佢想推嘅posts一次過慢慢推上嚟，直到4點31分。期間剩係時事台就已經合共推咗15個posts(如果計埋其他台應該多3~4個到)。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/xzECMy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FxzECMy.png&h=c77ce048&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/ekGtL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FekGtL8.png&h=83e571cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/LP2iXw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FLP2iXw.png&h=8e01950d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/XnHTFu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FXnHTFu.png&h=a000213a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/O2Tf3D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FO2Tf3D.png&h=6bbc4745&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/WeZMuO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FWeZMuO.png&h=d872348b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/ILmPdx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FILmPdx.png&h=f4b92719&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/dpxNZg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FdpxNZg.png&h=b4669602&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/SB1iO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FSB1iO9.png&h=90010ce7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/tPbFe2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FtPbFe2.png&h=ab90c53a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/ZXLOMp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FZXLOMp.png&h=9e6a9eb1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/7eRM1O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F7eRM1O.png&h=ef3c5d9b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/cqTg31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FcqTg31.png&h=0ef72481&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/Fxy1rj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FFxy1rj.png&h=05a82afd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/VyJrip.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FVyJrip.png&h=2de1a0b9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/QFfl7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FQFfl7B.png&h=feb66d3b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/ENWuBn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FENWuBn.png&h=aab618f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/dCbXS2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FdCbXS2.png&h=005d54ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最終成個下畫時事台都成日見到 做個快樂人 (#301682) 嘅posts。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/tLJGbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FtLJGbB.jpg&h=c4b394ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/yuNko4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FyuNko4.jpg&h=74d717db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddd2a998714617142f33c6f598e4b5a92888c721","tid":715563,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:47:45.000Z","msg":"而會員莘辛學子 (#596295) 同 戀屍神父 (#583602)就分別大約喺夜晚8點同10點瘋狂推posts做個快樂人(#301682)3個月內不同台嘅posts。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/yh9ePR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2Fyh9ePR.png&h=b521222b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/qKVDS9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FqKVDS9.png&h=57327276&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/etiBK9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FetiBK9.png&h=e4a538bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/9BFORP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F9BFORP.png&h=a3dc9ace&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/CRnshO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FCRnshO.png&h=7f7b087f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最終時事台夜晚搞到頭嗰版7成都係佢嘅posts。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/06/24/hmBM3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2FhmBM3c.jpg&h=948e5a6b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢幾日見巴打們嘈得最多嘅係點解要bam會員做個快樂人 (#301682)。我見到好多唔同類型嘅理由 : 又話係因為佢講嘅嘢太變態、又話係佢因為開分身、又話佢出posts開錯台、又話係因為佢洗板。佢係咪分身，呢啲嘢只有admin先會知，我當佢唔係先 ; 而出posts開錯台，有會員指正話只會刪posts ; 講嘢太變態可追究，唔係不嬲都有官非先會刪咩?最後洗板，佢確實係有惡意洗板喎，而洗板渣正嚟做係真係要bam。至於另外兩位會員，好明顯係有心想攬抄，洗板佢哋都有份。咁結果好簡單啫，如果admin bam做個快樂人 (#301682)嘅理由係因為洗板，咁佢哋理所當然地都應該一齊bam。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6921211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCA%26message%3D6921211&d=%2B07ZEybtJ%2Fh79VOJ5xHweROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d8878b72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CA&amp;message=6921211</a>"},{"pid":"7ab6cbea39c876dc570264f12fb540a76c755b62","tid":715563,"uid":4880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"關連登撚事"},{"pid":"40d3d010a06d98d9266753b837713d027753e165","tid":715563,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T10:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}